    "body": "The issue is caused by how the openfoam-org upstream decided _their_ internal name for `aarch64`.\r\n\r\nTimeline:\r\n- Dec-2017 : ARM64 support was added to openfoam.com (for the v1712 release)\r\n- Jan-2018 : added support for ARM64 to the spack package.\r\n- Jun-2020 : Arm64 support was added to openfoam.org\r\n\r\nThis unnecessary incompatibility has prompted a few users to attempt various solutions (#19622, #19743, #17906). Unfortunately they all add too much code bloat, potential breakage etc.",
